org.springframework.format.datetime

Class DateTimeFormatAnnotationFormatterFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.springframework.context.support.EmbeddedValueResolutionSupport
      • org.springframework.format.datetime.DateTimeFormatAnnotationFormatterFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Aware, EmbeddedValueResolverAware, AnnotationFormatterFactory<DateTimeFormat>

    public class DateTimeFormatAnnotationFormatterFactory
extends EmbeddedValueResolutionSupport
implements AnnotationFormatterFactory<DateTimeFormat>
    Formats fields annotated with the DateTimeFormat annotation using a DateFormatter.
    Since:
    3.2
    Author:
    Phillip Webb, Sam Brannen
    See Also:

        Description copied from interface: AnnotationFormatterFactory
        Get the Printer to print the value of a field of fieldType annotated with annotation.

        If the type T the printer accepts is not assignable to fieldType, a coercion from fieldType to T will be attempted before the Printer is invoked.
